{"tid":1375948,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"務必置頂！預備運動最後全面升級，聯結國內，引發全國茉莉花革命！","createTime":"2019-07-28T07:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:23:16.000Z","uid":130402,"like":170,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ca9468dffda2d58a8721b91bc7a84a3954f845","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"這個幾個月大家在這場運動都做得非常不錯，對比以往抗爭運動，這次明顯智慧是高出很多，不論是和理非和勇武派，文宣組等都發揮出令全港及海外國家一致稱贊的效果<br />\n<br />\n我地呢場運動發酵到而家，氣氛同環境對於抗爭革命已經越黎越成熟，但係我地有時會拘泥於形式上的本土運動，大眾似乎未意識到即使本土民主成功，中共統治下，我地既民主制度絕不能長治久安，這是顯然的。更莫講大眾有機會因港府決定成立獨調or釋義士等讓步而選擇妥協令運動失力，始終港人對民主自決的慾望是有限的。<br />\n<br />\n我地港人一直呼籲台灣萬萬不能接受一國兩制，但人地國家一開始已有健全的民主自由制，加上有海峽及國軍保護，我們依然苦勸台人絕不能接受一國兩制，可見我們意識中是對「一國兩制」全面絕望的，但我們自身卻仍在此制度下爭取不可一見的民主自由制度，無疑是水中撈月。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地要把握機會，藉住呢次大運動的推進，一步一步將反共的抗爭意念推及中國各地，務必要全面引起全國的革命思潮。任重而道遠，這事不簡單，也不易達成，但以其目的性來說，理應是這場運動最後，也是最重要的升級。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一天不反共，一天休想民主</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif?ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif%3Fssl%3D1&h=698e13c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下，我將抱磚引玉，為大家研討下一步的做法和思路"},{"pid":"2dcf092e9aced7d05a0f99cc291994324260a556","tid":1375948,"uid":185416,"like":70,"dislike":9,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"深圳河以北唔關我事"},{"pid":"f9c3d3cf302f3e1d738c6212d4084ed78fa4dc71","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"這幾天夢遊了很多次，勇完了，也須要在鍵盤上為大家談一些運動上更重要的方向"},{"pid":"8e87be49e10e77eb060e6ec9032a661b04915c2f","tid":1375948,"uid":126889,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"聯華反華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各有各做啦"},{"pid":"8d5b44f0f18633e7a2470fcd16a9a0d049d0114b","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4aWW0c79T-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4aWW0c79T-k&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpwhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=258cb007\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4aWW0c79T-k</a><br />\n大家可由11:56開始睇<br />\n但重點是19:49開始"},{"pid":"b4a04b9151b3c65961e59e5c5d38d604ea160922","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e87be49e10e77eb060e6ec9032a661b04915c2f","tid":1375948,"uid":126889,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"聯華反華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各有各做啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"當然當然，不然的話我就不會在這場運動中文武兩邊拼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油"},{"pid":"42d1e79b3216af0823c75c5f7d3241b0d86bc980","tid":1375948,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"國內?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe6c341fc9c92c9029d5e6f1412ce12bba0c8f4","tid":1375948,"uid":126889,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b4a04b9151b3c65961e59e5c5d38d604ea160922","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e87be49e10e77eb060e6ec9032a661b04915c2f","tid":1375948,"uid":126889,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"聯華反華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各有各做啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"當然當然，不然的話我就不會在這場運動中文武兩邊拼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"有D人覺得中國唔關我地事 但個人覺得做左無不可"},{"pid":"dba792ed35310ef3c23a77ee55d44935b42e99d4","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"談回正題，明居正係台灣很知名的台大政治學榮譽教授<br />\n佢既團隊「透視中國」亦都係一流既中國內外部分析預測團隊，入面有不少學家，專家，甚至乎大陸共產黨既官員幫助分析<br />\n起中美未打貿易戰之前，明居正已經預測到好多事，而分析左唔少美國對華政策在大體上有何轉變及中共有咩反擊措施(但好多都係損人100，自扣3000)，甚至乎早在習近平剛上位既時候，已經預測佢會以「反貪腐」為名去奪權，幾個月後已成真。<br />\n所以佢既分析絕對值得大家一睇"},{"pid":"3846ec54a9a0be45debad1ee8622a62b399922b3","tid":1375948,"uid":60749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbe6c341fc9c92c9029d5e6f1412ce12bba0c8f4","tid":1375948,"uid":126889,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b4a04b9151b3c65961e59e5c5d38d604ea160922","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e87be49e10e77eb060e6ec9032a661b04915c2f","tid":1375948,"uid":126889,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"聯華反華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各有各做啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"當然當然，不然的話我就不會在這場運動中文武兩邊拼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"有D人覺得中國唔關我地事 但個人覺得做左無不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"同兄弟爬山同理<br />\n有人覺得work 只要目標一樣 咪去做<br />\n咁你有你做 我有我做 <br />\n可以幫到手又唔太影響到自己 咪幫"},{"pid":"9d883cb2e19dceeb9b9824cbd1860d173c4beb0c","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"42d1e79b3216af0823c75c5f7d3241b0d86bc980","tid":1375948,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"國內?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"我知大家對大陸有好多唔同主觀情緒<br />\n但係搞運動有時要識得站高看，放下無謂執著<br />\n以長遠目標來說，我們要贏得最後勝利，國內是絕對target！"},{"pid":"8b4628deb3e62bf3b771dce35697c372600372a4","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"以第一步來說，文宣組巴打們是走不掉的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地開頭起九站西大遊行已經做過類似功夫，就係以airdrop同傳單宣傳本土運動<br />\n初頭我好興奮，估唔到大家咁醒已經準備散播革命種子予大陸人<br />\n但係我在睇傳單內容，就知道走錯了小小方向（但運動總不會事事精準有效，所以大家絕不須介懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n我地向陸客宣傳既內容，起始點係我去解釋我地港人點解遊行，目的係咩，詳情係點。但大陸人思維上是不太重視的，大部分陸客黎香港都係想「購物」，甚至唔少人潛意識都睇唔起香港，覺得香港人係搞事，要搞港獨，更甚是誤解我地係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「反華反中」</span></span><br />\n跟據我多年分析了解，中共為免自己既暴政引起國內人既不滿憤慨情緒而導致政權不穩，往往都會動用大量官媒煽動「民族主義」，以大中國人被外國勢力逼害為名，將國內人長年既不滿同憤恨情緒轉至對西方國家既仇恨，所以我地往往睇到國內官媒到處攻擊外國，話人地點點點，成日好似被逼害妄想咁到處喊苦喊怒。不難見，佢地生活相當充實，早上恨美帝，中午恨日本，晚上恨台獨，要食宵夜便順道恨港獨<br />\n我地要好好利用呢種<strong><em>「民族自大情緒」</em></strong>為宣傳方向<br />\n我下面再講"},{"pid":"7ad3ad4bdbc4826e73239857c2f22ae69befb957","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2dcf092e9aced7d05a0f99cc291994324260a556","tid":1375948,"uid":185416,"like":70,"dislike":9,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"深圳河以北唔關我事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"我地冇海峽保護，我地香港緊接住大陸，避不開了<br />\n我也討厭部分大陸人，但運動唔可以太短視，一日唔反共，我地香港就永不能自保<br />\n一切運動成功後，再談對中政策也不遲<br />\n但現在，是絕對有必要聯結國內人的"},{"pid":"0f4e5f8d0efa2bfacd0b3bc9984872b50d9fc4b5","tid":1375948,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:35:33.000Z","msg":"幫一幫推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8629998b6ff21f6c5f8da04aa53a30f828ecde","tid":1375948,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FX62ts8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFX62ts8.jpg&h=54fa1f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民頭盔 可以<br />\n1)每人一物資, 唔怕比人充公<br />\n2)有noise<br />\n3)比狗逗可以串番佢 [就係警察保護唔到市民,我地先要自己保護自己, 仲好意思問戴頭盔做咩, 知唔知醜]<br />\n4)人人都戴 減低黑警搜市民裝備<br />\n5)同埋不幸有恐襲可以自保39分鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n[抗議警黑合作] 全民港鐵戴頭盔 全民出街戴頭盔 日常<br />\n- 分享自 